### MicroPay API smoke tests (run with REST Client plugins or convert to Postman)

@host = http://localhost

### Register user
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "portfolio-user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "Portfolio",
  "lastName": "User"
}

###
### Login user
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "portfolio-user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###
### Template calls below: replace {{token}} and {{userId}} from login response

### Get wallet
GET {{host}}/api/wallet/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Credit wallet
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/{{userId}}/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500,
  "transactionId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000cafe"
}

### Debit wallet
POST {{host}}/api/wallet/{{userId}}/debit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50,
  "transactionId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-00000000feed"
}

### Create payment
POST {{host}}/api/payment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payerUserId": "{{userId}}",
  "payeeUserId": "{{userId}}",
  "amount": 25,
  "currency": "INR",
  "reference": "portfolio-smoke"
}

### List transactions
GET {{host}}/api/transactions/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List notifications
GET {{host}}/api/notifications/{{userId}}?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


